<p><a href="http://ubuntusatanic.org/">Ubuntu Satanic Edition (SE)</a> is a Linux distribution based on Ubuntu.</p>

<p>The Devil alwas did have the best tunes‚Ä¶</p>

<p>Ubuntu Satanic Edition is a community developed, Linux-based operating system combining the best software and the heaviest music on one CD. Many applications are included, plus thousands more available to download and install at the click of a button. And it‚Äôs all completely free.</p>

