<p>The dark theme plunges your desktop into depths of Hell, while the ray-traced screensaver keeps your PC looking evil even when you‚Äôre not using it.</p>

<p>The CD also contains a 30 minute EP of the best creative-commons licensed heavy metal music from the likes of StabWounD, Auvernia, Frontside, Skaut, Taste of Hell, Scape.Goat and Holy Pain.</p>

<p>SE can either be run from the CD or installed to your computer using the graphical installer. On a typical computer the installation should take you less than 25 minutes. It is built on top of Ubuntu 8.04, so check out the Ubuntu site for a full list of features.
