<p>If you already have Ubuntu installed, you can simply add the packages by following these instructions.
Using the Live CD</p>

<p>You can run Ubuntu Satanic Edition straight off the Live CD. Please note that due to the slow speed of CDs it may take a while to boot up. Please be patient, it‚Äôs worth it! Once booted, you should have access to a fully functional PC including Firefox 3 for surfing the web. There will be an icon on the desktop entitled ‚ÄúMusic for the Damned‚Äù. Double clicking on this will display the tracks from the EP. Move the mouse over them or double-click to play.</p>

